        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。初始状态是从ContentCDN创建目标进入active状态对吗？然后active可以分出三条分支：暂停、取消和完成？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "active",
        "Create Goal",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Pause Goal",
        "Cancel Goal",
        "Complete Goal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，active是默认状态。但要注意取消操作是由ClassroomService负责的，而完成操作需要StudentDB参与。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "active",
        "cancelled",
        "completed",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经画出了active的三个出口。现在处理paused状态——从active暂停后，应该也能取消或完成吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "active",
        "paused",
        "Resume Goal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，paused可以恢复回active，也可以取消或完成。不过这里有个细节：paused状态下的取消由ContentCDN处理，完成则由LMS Portal负责，和active状态不一样。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "paused",
        "active",
        "cancelled",
        "completed",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Resume Goal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：active的取消是ClassroomService，paused的取消是ContentCDN？这是业务上刻意设计的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "active",
        "paused",
        "cancelled",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，active时取消需要课堂服务介入验证，paused时取消相对简单，直接走内容分发网络。另外completed和cancelled都是终态，completed最终汇聚到LMS Portal，cancelled汇聚到StudentDB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "completed",
        "cancelled",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Final State"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "状态流转已经画完了。我注意到每个状态的业务特性很重要，需要加注释说明吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "active",
        "paused",
        "completed",
        "cancelled"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要。active要说明是默认状态、可更新进度、有截止日期倒计时；paused要强调进度保留、倒计时暂停、可随时恢复。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "active",
        "paused",
        "Default status",
        "Deadline countdown",
        "Progress preserved"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。completed和cancelled作为终态，注释需要体现什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
