    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "所有注释都加好了。让我再核对一遍：ContentCDN创建目标，ClassroomService负责active时的取消，StudentDB负责active时的完成和cancelled的终态，LMS Portal负责paused时的完成和completed的终态。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
